<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:25:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示全球经济增长弹性与降息预期不符</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社调查的数百名经济学家对今年和明年全球增长前景的乐观情绪正在增强，尽管他们坚持降息预测，但风险仍然倾向于通胀上升。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于快餐价格上涨损害了需求，麦当劳公布了疲弱的季度业绩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</link><description>麦当劳周一报告销售额意外下降，季度利润未达到华尔街预期，因为菜单价格上涨，这家汉堡巨头难以吸引现金短缺的顾客选择在家吃饭。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：比较平静，但能持续多久？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-29/</link><description>欧洲、中东和非洲地区财经与市场突发新闻记者 Alun John 对美国和全球市场的未来展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>跳水——中国杨、连夺得男子双人10米跳台冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国选手杨浩/连俊杰在男子双人10米跳台比赛中夺得金牌，锁定跳水八枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>射击——中国选手盛在巴黎奥运会上夺得第二枚金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国选手盛立浩在男子10米气步枪比赛中获胜，夺得了他在巴黎奥运会上的第二枚金牌，而韩国选手潘孝珍则赢得了女子金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>香港维权人士擅自带出监狱投诉表格被定罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一判定民主活动人士周文豪和他的律师胡菲丽丝去年未经授权将一份供监察员使用的投诉表格带出监狱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美日在海上问题和军事扩张问题上的“不实指控”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，美国和日本之间的联合声明在海上问题上“错误地指责”中国，并指责中国正常的军事发展和国防政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国7月份制造业活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，中国7月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，由于旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累经济增长，官员们需要推出进一步刺激措施的预期依然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，台湾第二季度经济增长放缓，但受到人工智能热潮的支撑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，尽管人工智能技术的高需求推动了出口强劲，但依赖贸易的台湾第二季度经济增长可能放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-q2-economic-growth-seen-slowing-supported-by-ai-boom-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲因鸽派利率希望而反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长谴责危险的南海行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</link><description>澳大利亚、印度、日本和美国外长周一表示，他们对南中国海的恐吓和危险行为感到严重关切，并承诺加强该地区的海上安全。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>法院称碧桂园清算听证会推迟至明年一月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求碧桂园清算请愿书的听证会推迟至 2025 年 1 月 20 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商有了喘息的机会，该开发商正试图敲定离岸债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>债权人寻求破产程序后，中国恒大的电动汽车部门下线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一早盘，中国恒大新能源汽车股价下跌 7%，此前该公司旗下两家子公司的个人债权人寻求法院批准这些子公司进入破产程序并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行和美联储政策决定前日元保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-nikkei-jumps-central-bank-meetings-loom-2024-07-29/</link><description>日元周一保持稳定，由于利率预期转变和股市抛售，日元出现自 4 月底以来的最佳单周涨幅，市场情绪仍然脆弱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:31:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-eases-nikkei-jumps-central-bank-meetings-loom-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商CATL第二季度利润增长更快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国电动汽车电池巨头宁德时代第二季度利润增长更快，尽管全球最大汽车市场的电动汽车需求放缓，而地缘政治紧张局势给其海外扩张蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 11:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>